{"tid":1853580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「醫護唔會復工」求人開工要有求人嘅語氣，林鄭根本無。籌碼係我地手，贏硬。","createTime":"2020-01-31T05:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:54:22.000Z","uid":126621,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcd0b191a8d3348d8eae974888a4507793a0f0a","tid":1853580,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=90df07d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span>"},{"pid":"72c14eec4e79b6459ff3d9de698adf5bd18e0aa8","tid":1853580,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"602b7b4b688cf4ecb97e1405b45eaf062dbe0e72","tid":1853580,"uid":34189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"立辱醫護罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加條阻醫辦公法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即撥錢俾OT錢同去外國買生化裝甲救護車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護做嘢唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4b2aacc592d2e0c341f3b0c8c7c95415111fd2","tid":1853580,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"602b7b4b688cf4ecb97e1405b45eaf062dbe0e72","tid":1853580,"uid":34189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"立辱醫護罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加條阻醫辦公法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即撥錢俾OT錢同去外國買生化裝甲救護車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護做嘢唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:21:51.000Z","msg":"合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e953e4196a8c1303c55ec83002a005e23af7df","tid":1853580